## 2Ô∏è‚É£ Linux System Internals (Very Important)

Because your project is Linux-specific.

Learn:

* How Linux users work
* Permissions (chmod, chown)
* /etc/passwd
* /etc/shadow
* sudo
* Cron jobs
* SSH
* Process lifecycle
* What happens when you run a command
* Syscalls (basic idea)

Without this, you cannot understand logs.

---

## 3Ô∏è‚É£ Linux Logging System

