# üìä LAYER 3 ‚Äî Detection & Analytics Thinking

Now we move into intelligence.

---

## 7Ô∏è‚É£ What is UEBA?

Learn:

* Behavioral baselines
* Anomaly detection
* What is ‚Äúnormal‚Äù vs ‚Äúabnormal‚Äù
* Time-window based analysis

Understand:

If user logs in 1 time/day normally,
and suddenly logs in 20 times ‚Üí anomaly.

---

## 8Ô∏è‚É£ Correlation Logic

Learn:

* Time-window grouping
* Entity linking (user, IP, host)
* Attack chains
* MITRE ATT&CK framework (high-level)

You must understand:

A single log is weak.
Multiple related logs = incident.

